So, Josh, you've seen a lot of students go do this program. What's your advice?

5
00:00:11,390 --> 00:00:15,169
Yeah. So, I think one of the the biggest things is,

6
00:00:15,169 --> 00:00:16,454
to be successful in the program,

7
00:00:16,454 --> 00:00:18,894
you have to be a really active learner.

8
00:00:18,894 --> 00:00:22,870
What that means is, not just watching all the videos,

