00:00:26,945 --> 00:00:28,120
and they take really good notes,

11
00:00:28,120 --> 00:00:33,219
so whether that's like screenshots of the videos and then written notes underneath,

12
00:00:33,219 --> 00:00:35,810
type out notes or for me,

13
00:00:35,810 --> 00:00:39,755
I actually like just writing things in a notepad that I carry around with me,

14
00:00:39,755 --> 00:00:42,120
and then I can look at later.

15
00:00:42,119 --> 00:00:44,619
Also, just when there's coding,

16
00:00:44,619 --> 00:00:46,154
writing the code yourself.

