00:01:02,450 --> 00:01:07,159
a very tricky component that has a big contribution to success.

23
00:01:07,159 --> 00:01:09,530
But what we've seen is that students who are most

24
00:01:09,530 --> 00:01:13,030
successful come to the classroom at least two times a week.

25
00:01:13,030 --> 00:01:15,484
So, just making sure you make that habit

